metadata.name: Light of the World
metadata.description:
Since the dawn of the universe, the world has known the vacuum, it has known darkness. Even as the age of man began, through their deeds, darkness continued to reign.

For light to rule, no I, we, must be the light that will push the darkness. We must be a beacon the will brighten each other's lives as well as our world.

I think we can.

Dimensions:
18x24 In. 250ppi.
PNG Format.
Feb, 2022.
